{"type":"message","id":"d7a8a0ec","parentId":"2b248933","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:09:09.893Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"晚上好，Sir。🎩 我是贾维斯，已就绪待命。\n\n我看到您提到 OpenClaw Control Center 的界面显示\"未连接\"，左侧导航为空。让我先检查一下 Gateway 服务的状态，看看是什么情况。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw gateway status","ask":"on-miss"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":833,"output":76,"cacheRead":39748,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773760145762}}
