{"type":"message","id":"7e370dbd","parentId":"ef6da95f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:10:32.573Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了，Sir。您说的是这个 **OpenClaw Control Center** 界面——您希望我根据这些\"员工\"（智能体）的名称和职责，**实际创建和配置这些功能**。\n\n我看到您已经定义了6个智能体角色：\n- **May** - 核心主控\n- **Gock** - 每日新闻\n- **Otter** - 私人助理\n- **Pandas** - 开发测试\n- **Monkey** - 内容创作\n- **Tiger** - 安全更新\n\n这些目前只是界面展示，需要我帮您：\n1. **创建实际的智能体配置文件**\n2. **设置它们的定时任务和自动化流程**\n3. **配置每个角色的具体功能**\n\n您想从哪个开始？还是希望我全部搭建起来？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":4202,"output":164,"cacheRead":38144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42510,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773760225188}}
{"type":"message","id":"dd79d64f","parentId":"7e370dbd","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:10:57.629Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-17 23:10 GMT+8] 这个右上角都是未连接 然后左侧的导航里面都没有东西功能 你要根据取名然后自己创建需要的功能啊"}],"timestamp":1773760257627}}
{"type":"message","id":"50cd0a1b","parentId":"dd79d64f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:11:02.269Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了，Sir。我来处理这两个问题：\n\n1. **右上角\"未连接\"** - 需要修复 WebUI 与 Gateway 的连接\n2. **左侧导航为空** - 需要根据您定义的6个智能体（May、Gock、Otter、Pandas、Monkey、Tiger）创建实际功能\n\n让我先检查一下 Gateway 配置，然后为每个智能体创建功能模块。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"gateway:7","name":"gateway","arguments":{"action":"config.get"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:8","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\cron-mastery\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":331,"output":133,"cacheRead":40704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41168,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773760257629}}
